---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Logo from '../components/Logo.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — MoodSketch" description="MoodSketch privacy policy. We don't collect your data.">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-light-rule">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between">
      <Logo variant="dark" size={24} textSize="1rem" />
      <a href="https://moodsketch.app" class="text-sm text-sketch-gray hover:text-ink transition-colors">← Back</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pt-28 pb-20">
    <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-ink mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sketch-gray mb-10">Last updated: February 26, 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-ink/80 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">The short version</h2>
        <p>MoodSketch does not collect, transmit, or store any personal data. Everything you draw stays on your device.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">What we collect</h2>
        <p><strong>Nothing.</strong> MoodSketch stores your sketches and mood tags locally on your device using your browser's localStorage. No data is sent to any server. No account is required. No analytics are collected.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Local storage</h2>
        <p>The app uses your device's local storage to save:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Your daily sketches (stored as image data)</li>
          <li>Mood tags you've added to sketches</li>
          <li>Your streak count and last draw date</li>
          <li>Your onboarding status and reminder time preference</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">This data never leaves your device. Uninstalling the app or clearing your browser data will delete it permanently.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Third-party services</h2>
        <p>MoodSketch does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking services. We do not use cookies for tracking purposes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>MoodSketch does not collect personal information from anyone, including children under 13. The app is safe for all ages.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>If this policy changes, we'll update the date at the top of this page. Since we don't collect data, we don't anticipate meaningful changes.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@sketchkit.app" class="text-mood-coral hover:underline">hello@sketchkit.app</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
